  "texts": [
    "Alter Fig. 3 An example of Evaluation Metric 1 for when comparing two lists of Compound messages.",
    "Three failure modes at the Compound message level, \"Addition\", \"Removal\", and \"Alteration\" are colored green, yellow, and blue, respectively.",
    "Underscored fields denote failures at the leaf fields level (Evaluation Metric 2, vide infra).",
    "Data shown is for illustration purposes only.",
    "scored) are considered as \"Alteration\" (value), and \"Addition\" (reaction_role), respectively."
